If metal braces will be removed before end of enrollment period, mark to Yes call back.

If metal braces will not be removed before end of enrollment period, permanent metal retainer, or metal dental implant that is clearly contraindication, mark No call back. 

If parent is unsure, ask for their best guess, mark to Yes call back.

name: fc_p_vs__indselfrel_001
label: People should learn how to take care of themselves and not depend on others. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__indselfrel_002
label: The most important thing parents can teach their children is to be independent from others. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__indselfrel_003
label: As children get older their parents should allow them to make their own decisions. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__indselfrel_004
label: When there are problems in life, a person can only count on themself. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__indselfrel_005
label: Parents should encourage children to solve their own problems. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__obl_001
label: Children should be taught that it is their duty to care for their parents when their parents get old. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__obl_002
label: If a relative is having a hard time financially, one should help them out if possible. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__obl_003
label: A person should share their home with relatives if they need a place to stay. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__obl_004
label: Older kids should take care of and be role models for their younger brothers and sisters. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__obl_005
label: Parents should be willing to make great sacrifices to make sure their children have a better life. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__ref_001
label: Children should always do things to make their parents happy. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__ref_002
label: When it comes to important decisions, the family should ask for advice from close relatives. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__ref_003
label: Children should be taught to always be good because they represent the family. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__ref_004
label: A person should always think about their family when making important decisions. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__ref_005
label: It is important to work hard and do one's best because this work reflects on the family. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_001
label: One's belief in God or Higher Power(s) gives inner strength and meaning to life. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_002
label: God or Higher Power(s) is first; family is second. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_003
label: Parents should teach their children how to pray. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_004
label: If everything is taken away, one still has their faith in God or Higher Power(s). [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_005
label: It is important to thank God or Higher Power(s) every day for all one has. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_006
label: It is important to follow the Word of God or Higher Power(s). [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__relig_007
label: Religion should be an important part of one's life. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__supp_001
label: Parents should teach their children that the family always comes first. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__supp_002
label: Family provides a sense of security because they will always be there for you. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__supp_003
label: It is always important to be united as a family. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__supp_004
label: It is important to have close relationships with aunts/uncles, grandparents, and cousins. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__supp_005
label: Holidays and celebrations are important because the whole family comes together. [Parent]

name: fc_p_vs__supp_006
label: It is important for family members to show their love and affection to one another. [Parent]
